ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectAgreement on Tax Cooperation and the Exchange of Information relating to Taxes between Canada and the Republic of Panama
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to sign, or to delegate powers to sign, on behalf of Canada, subject to ratification, the AGREEMENT between Canada and the REPUBLIC OF PANAMA for TAX COOPERATION AND THE EXCHANGE OF INFORMATION RELATING TO TAXES.
